---+++ GUMS

I copied the STAR group mappings prescription from
[[http://osg.ivdgl.org/twiki/bin/view/Provisioning/GumsTemplate][http://osg.ivdgl.org/twiki/bin/view/Provisioning/GumsTemplate]]
including the 
&lt;verbatim&gt;
&lt;!--- 9 STAR ---!&gt;
&lt;/verbatim&gt;
and got an error when doing the &quot;Update Members&quot; from the GUMS web interface 
&lt;verbatim&gt; (!https://somehost:8443/gums) &lt;/verbatim&gt;.  The error in the admin log file 
($VDT_LOCATION/tomcat/v5/logs/gums-service-admin.log)
said&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;
01 Jul 2005 15:05:25,668 [FATAL]: The configuration wasn&#39;t read properly. GUMS is not 
operational: The string &quot;--&quot; is not permitted within comments.
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

I needed to change the !sslCertfile and !sslKey values from&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;/etc/grid-security/host{cert|key}.pem&lt;/tt&gt; to &lt;tt&gt;/etc/grid-security/http/http{cert|key}.pem&lt;/tt&gt;

